OL,7,FITV Meridian reporter Kara Digby has
OL,8,Fbeen to meet Lukas at the cafe
OL,9,Foffering life-changing opportunities
OL,11,FA charity in Oxfordshire is calling
OL,12,Ffor employers to do more to get people
OL,13,Fwith learning disabilities into the
OL,14,Fworld of work.JYellow Submarine, which
OL,15,Fhas cafes in Oxford and Witney, is
OL,16,Foffering people living with autism and
OL,17,Fother additional needs the chance to
OL,18,Fboost their skills, confidence and
OL,19,Fshow what they can offer.
