OL,7,FLukas Blake is 22 and is one of the
OL,8,Fmembers of staff in Oxford. He has
OL,9,Fautism and told ITV News Meridian
OL,10,Ffinding employment can often be a
OL,11,Fdisappointing and stressful experience.
OL,13,FAll trainees have a minimum of 3
OL,14,Fshifts a week, with one day a week in
OL,15,Fthe classroom to help them towards
OL,16,Femployment. It's unpaid, but is
OL,17,Fclassed as an education course.
OL,19,FLukas is on a traineeship in the cafe,
OL,20,Fwhich helps to bridge the gap between
OL,21,Feducation and employment
