OL,7,FAccording to the charity Yellow
OL,8,FSubmarine's impact report only around
OL,9,F5% of adults with a learning
OL,10,Fdisability are in employment.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, the National Autistic
OL,13,FSociety says 78% of adults with autism
OL,14,Fare unemployed.
OL,16,FYellow Submarine says: "...We believe
OL,17,Fthat everyone can make a valuable
OL,18,Fcontribution to the workforce.
