OL,7,F"Using our cafes, we provide training
OL,8,Fand support to transition our trainees
OL,9,Finto appropriate and sustainable
OL,10,Femployment.
OL,12,F"We remove barriers to work and
OL,13,Fchallenge preconceptions so our
OL,14,Ftrainees can thrive and reach their
OL,15,Ffull potential."
OL,17,FThe charity says 58% of their trainees
OL,18,Fthat have a learning disability moved
OL,19,Fstraight into paid employment and only
OL,20,F6% of our trainees with autism did not
OL,21,Fsecure employment.
